WorkItem.Description:
If you have a simple method like so:

```
test() {
	try {
	}
	catch (e) {
	}
}
```

And then press Ctrl-K,D a couple of times, it'll end up looking like this:

```
test() {
						try {
						}
						catch (e) {
						}
}
```

This is using the a personal build of typescriptServices.js from the latest code from the `develop` branch.
